 F[x]=\{a_0+a_1x+a_2x^2+\cdots+a_nx^n\mid a_0,\ldots,a_n\in F,\ n\in\mathbb{N}\}. 
\tag{1} f(x)=b_0+b_1x+\cdots+b_nx^n,\qquad g(x)=c_0+c_1x+\cdots+c_nx^n 
\tag{2} (\alpha\cdot f)(x):=\alpha\cdot f(x)=\alpha b_0+\alpha b_1x+\cdots+\alpha b_nx^n 
\tag{3} (f+g)(x):=f(x)+g(x)=(b_0+c_0)+(b_1+c_1)x+\cdots+(b_n+c_n)x^n. 
