f
g
\alpha\cdot f
f+g
\phi_1
 \phi_1(\alpha\cdot f)=\alpha\cdot\phi_1(f)\qquad\text{and}\qquad \phi_1(f+g)=\phi_1(f)+\phi_1(g) 
